casebody.data:
Rochelle DRIESSEN, etc., Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
UNIVERSITY OF MIAMI SCHOOL OF LAW, et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1754 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 15, 2017 EMAS, LOGUE and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Following review of the response, it is ordered that appellee Emily C. Moises Day Training Center's motion to dismiss appeal is granted, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed for lack of jurisdiction. The order on appeal is a non-final, non-appealable order.

Appellant's motion for extension and/or enlargement of time to file an initial brief is hereby denied as moot.
